onien" lang="mk" hreflang="mk" class="interlanguage-link-target">Македонски</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ml"><a href="https://ml.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%B4%AA%E0%B4%BE%E0%B4%B5%E0%B4%99%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%99%E0%B5%BE_(%E0%B4%B2%E0%B5%86_%E0%B4%AE%E0%B4%BF%E0%B4%B8%E0%B5%87%E0%B4%B1%E0%B4%BE%E0%B4%AC%E0%B5%8D%E0%B4%B2%E0%B5%86)" title="പാവങ്ങൾ (ലെ മിസേറാബ്ലെ) — malayalam" lang="ml" hreflang="ml" class="interlanguage-link-target">മലയാളം</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ms"><a href="https://ms.wikipedia.org/wiki/Les_Mis%C3%A9rables" title="Les Misérables — malais" lang="ms" hreflang="ms" class="interlanguage-link-target">Bahasa Melayu</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nl"><a href="https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Les_Mis%C3%A9rables_(boek)" title="Les Misérables (boek) — néerlandais" lang="nl" hreflang="nl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Nederlands</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-nn"><a href="https://nn.wikipedia.org/wiki/Les_Mis%C3%A9rables" title="Les Misérables — norvégien nynorsk" lang="nn" hreflang="nn" class="interlanguage-link-target">Norsk nynorsk</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-no"><a href="https://no.wikipedia.org/wiki/De_elendige" title="De elendige — norvégien bokmål" lang="nb" hreflang="nb" class="interlanguage-link-target">Norsk bokmål</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pa"><a href="https://pa.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%A8%A6%E0%A9%81%E0%A8%96%E0%A9%80%E0%A8%8F_(%E0%A8%A8%E0%A8%BE%E0%A8%B5%E0%A8%B2)" title="ਦੁਖੀਏ (ਨਾਵਲ) — pendjabi" lang="pa" hreflang="pa" class="interlanguage-link-target">ਪੰਜਾਬੀ</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pl badge-Q17437798 badge-goodarticle" title="bon article"><a href="https://pl.wikipedia.org/wiki/N%C4%99dznicy" title="Nędznicy — polonais" lang="pl" hreflang="pl" class="interlanguage-link-target">Polski</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-pt"><a href="https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Os_Miser%C3%A1veis" title="Os Miseráveis